== prompt 10 :: unit=rust_example.is_even+rust_example.is_odd :: pass=summary ==
You are analyzing a Rust function to create a summary of its behavior.


## Functions (mutually recursive group)

```
/// Mutual recursion: is_even delegates to is_odd.
pub fn is_even(n: i32) -> bool {
    if n == 0 {
        true
    } else {
        is_odd(n - 1)
    }
}
```

```
/// Mutual recursion: is_odd delegates to is_even.
pub fn is_odd(n: i32) -> bool {
    if n == 0 {
        false
    } else {
        is_even(n - 1)
    }
}
```


