== prompt 12 :: unit=rust_example.multiply :: pass=summary ==
You are analyzing a Rust function to create a summary of its behavior.

```
/// Multiplies two numbers by repeated addition.
pub fn multiply(a: i32, b: i32) -> i32 {
    let mut result = 0;
    for _ in 0..b {
        result = add(result, a);
    }
    result
}
```

